one day a big ship's engine stopped working. I mean BIG.... like cruise ship.
the crew couldnt figure it out, even after a week

the mechanic arrives and looks at the whole thing for an hour or two but he doesnt touch any thing
finally he goes to his tool box and pulls out a 5 ounce hammer
he approaches one of the many mechanical devices and gently taps it twice

the engine starts and runs smoothly
